General.Name: Novotek AB
General.Description: Novotek AB delivers solutions in the industrial IT and automation areas. The company designs, implements, deploys, and maintains its customers' systems for production management and control. It operates in Nordic, Benelux countries, Switzerland, the United Kingdom, and Ireland. The company was incorporated in 1955 and is headquartered in Malmö, Sweden.
